'''Qiluiy''' was a group of 3 [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90 corvettes]] used by the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]]. The three corvettes were part of a convoy which also consisted of 2 [[BFF-1 bulk freighter/Legends|BFF-1 bulk freighters]] called ''[[Xroi]]'' in the [[Mennaalii system]] which became under attack from pirates. However the pirate attack was driven off by Rebel [[T-65 X-wing starfighter/Legends|X-wings]], [[BTL Y-wing starfighter/Legends|Y-wings]] and [[RZ-1 A-wing interceptor/Legends|A-wings]].

